Title : You are supposed to own all your information on Facebook

Topic : Ownership

Summary : According to the Data use policy of Facebook, you always own all your information, and Facebook, when dealing with the personal data, removes the name or any other personally identifying information from it.

Score : I don't really know, since it's not sure how much such a declaration really worths...

--
